title: Coral Reefs, Haiti and Dominican Republic, World Resources Institute
name: Coral Reefs, Haiti and Dominican Republic, World Resources Institute
description:
A dataset of shallow water (generally less than 30 m depth) coral reef locations for the Caribbean Sea and Gulf of Mexico at 500 m resolution derived from a variety of sources. 
 
This dataset was developed for the Reefs at Risk Caribbean project (World Resources Institute, 2004 <http://reefsatrisk.wri.org>) and shows locations of coral reefs in the Wider Caribbean
